        "rich_text_rJaBdp": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Introduction",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Choosing the perfect <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-rings\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">engagement ring</span></a> is one of the most meaningful decisions you’ll make. Today’s trends focus on individuality, modern design, and conscious luxury. From timeless classics to bold contemporary styles, couples are choosing rings that reflect their personality and story.</p><p>At <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Lucira Jewelry</span></a>, we combine design-first thinking with ethically crafted lab-grown diamonds to create engagement rings that are elegant, meaningful, and made for modern love.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_qw7HLy": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1. Classic Solitaire Rings – Timeless Elegance That Never Fades",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>1. Classic Solitaire Rings – Timeless Elegance That Never Fades</h2>",
