        "rich_text_FczGG7": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p><a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/solitaire-rings\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Solitaire rings</span></a> remain the most iconic engagement ring style. Their minimal design highlights a single diamond, making them elegant, versatile, and forever relevant.</p><p>Why choose this style?<br/> If you prefer simplicity, timeless appeal, and maximum focus on the diamond’s brilliance, a solitaire ring is the perfect choice.</p><p>Example:<br/> The <em>Four Prong Round Solitaire Ring</em> and <em>Timeless Oval Solitaire Diamond Ring</em> from Lucira showcase how a single diamond can create a powerful and elegant statement.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
