          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Oval cut rings are loved for their elongated shape, which makes the diamond appear larger and more refined.</p><p>Why choose this style?<br/> If you want something modern yet elegant that enhances finger length and sparkle, oval rings are a great option.</p><p>Example:<br/> Lucira’s <em>Timeless Oval Solitaire Diamond Ring</em> is a perfect blend of contemporary design and classic beauty.</p>",
