        "rich_text_9LDfB8": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "6. Twist Band Rings – A Symbol of Two Lives Intertwined",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>6. Twist Band Rings – A Symbol of Two Lives Intertwined</h3><p>Twist band rings feature intertwined metal bands, symbolizing the union of two people.</p><p>Why choose this style?<br/> If you want a ring with deeper meaning and a romantic design, twist rings are a beautiful choice.</p><p>Example:<br/> The <em>Round Diamond Solitaire Twist Ring</em> from Lucira represents connection and harmony.</p>",
            "custom_id": "twist",
            "text_alignment": "left"
