          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "faq_question": "4.] Can Toi et Moi rings include gemstones?",
            "faq_answer": "<p>Yes. Some designs combine diamonds with coloured gemstones to add personal meaning.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_MUB7iF": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "faq_question": "5.] Are Toi et Moi rings a modern trend?",
            "faq_answer": "<p>The style actually dates back centuries but has recently become popular again because it feels both romantic and contemporary.</p>"
          }
        }
